# connect to bluetooth module on PI
sudo bluetoothctl 
agent on
default-agent
scan on
trust <<MAC>>
connect <<MAC>>
pair <<MAC>> 

If module bluetooth paired with PI before, then "connect" command will fail, type :
disconnect <<MAC>>
connect <<MAC>>
pair <<MAC>>

sudo rfcomm bind hci0 XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX 1
Now /dev/rfcomm0 was created

